OL,3,CThames Water discovers 312 storm
OL,4,Coverflows it didn't know it had
OL,6,FThree of England's biggest water
OL,7,Fcompanies are facing multimillion
OL,8,Fpound fines for dumping sewage, as ITV
OL,9,FNews Business and Economics Editor
OL,10,FJoel Hills reports
OL,12,FThe Brixton Storm Relief Sewer sits at
OL,13,Fthe foot of the MI6 building on the
OL,14,Fbanks of the river Thames.
OL,16,FLast year, this storm overflow spilt
OL,17,Fraw sewage into the river 130 times -
OL,18,Froughly one discharge every three days.
