OL,3,CThames Water discovers 312 storm
OL,4,Coverflows it didn't know it had
OL,6,FOfwat fined three companies for sewage
OL,7,Fdischarges on Tuesday but Thames Water
OL,8,Fis the worst offender.
OL,10,FThe regulator's investigation said
OL,11,FThames Water has consistently failed
OL,12,Fto monitor, operate, maintain, repair
OL,13,Fand upgrade its assets.
OL,15,FThe report highlights a lack of
OL,16,Finvestment but also a lack of care and
OL,17,Fcuriosity within the company -
OL,18,Fincluding at the board level.
