OL,3,CThames Water discovers 312 storm
OL,4,Coverflows it didn't know it had
OL,6,FThe investigation reveals that in
OL,7,F2022, Thames Water informed Ofwat it
OL,8,Fhad discovered 312 storm overflows it
OL,9,Fdidn't know existed and hadn't been
OL,10,Fmonitoring.
OL,12,FThames Water owns and operates 236
OL,13,Fwater treatment facilities, 157 are
OL,14,Fperforming so poorly that Thames
OL,15,FWaters considers them to be "sites of
OL,16,Fconcern".
OL,18,FUntreated sewage is being discharged
OL,19,Fbecause these plants cannot cope with
OL,20,Fthe volume of wastewater they need to
OL,21,Fprocess.
