OL,3,CThames Water discovers 312 storm
OL,4,Coverflows it didn't know it had
OL,6,FOfwat has fined Thames Water #104
OL,7,Fmillion and there may be more fines to
OL,8,Fcome. It has also proposed an
OL,9,F"enforcement" order which compels
OL,10,FThames Water to detail how it will
OL,11,Fimprove its network.
OL,13,FThames Water says it "takes this
OL,14,Fmatter very seriously", adding: "We
OL,15,Fregard all untreated discharges are
OL,16,Funacceptable, even when they are
OL,17,Fpermitted."
OL,19,FThe company can appeal the fine and it
OL,20,Fneeds the money.
