OL,6,FThe infrastructure is creaking and
OL,7,Fneeds upgrading.
OL,9,FLast month, Thames Water said it had
OL,10,Fenough cash to last until next May, by
OL,11,Fwhich time it needs to raise #750
OL,12,Fmillion from investors.
OL,14,FIf it can't, the company may be taken
OL,15,Finto "special administration", a form
OL,16,Fof temporary nationalisation.
